                       type=java.lang.Double.class)
public class ExternalTemperatureSILModel
extends ExternalTemperatureModel
    The class ExternalTemperatureSILModel extends the model class ExternalTemperatureModel to allow the model to log its messages on the owner component logger for software-in-the-loop tests.
